                        <i class="fas fa-question-circle"></i> How do I cancel my subscription?
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>You can cancel your subscription at any time through your device's App Store settings. Go to Settings > Apple ID > Subscriptions, find NextRole, and tap "Cancel Subscription". Your access will continue until the end of your current billing period.</p>
