                        <p>If you're experiencing issues with Apple Sign-In, try these steps:<br>
                        1. Make sure you're signed into your Apple ID in Settings<br>
                        2. Check your internet connection<br>
                        3. Restart the app and try again<br>
                        4. If the problem persists, try signing in with email instead</p>
